\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a nhau nh\u01b0ng \u00edt ra, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghe th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i. Ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i \u1ea5m \u00e1p, bi\u1ebft bi\u1ec3u l\u1ed9 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \u1ea5y, so v\u1edbi th\u01b0 tay hay nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng chat tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng, th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i bi\u1ebft bao nhi\u00eau.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 9X, 10X, h\u1eb3n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1edb nh\u1eefng b\u1ed1t \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng c\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thu\u1ed9c th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 7X, 8X, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 8X \u0111\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00ec l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 v\u00f4 v\u00e0n k\u1ec9 ni\u1ec7m g\u1eafn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ed1t \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i nh\u1ecf xinh n\u01a1i g\u00f3c ph\u1ed1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. &#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3173,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"video","meta":[],"categories":[14],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/tintuc6.ninhbinhweb.info\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/434"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/tintuc6.ninhbinhweb.info\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/tintuc6.ninhbinhweb.info\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/tintuc6.ninhbinhweb.info\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/tintuc6.ninhbinhweb.info\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=434"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/tintuc6.ninhbinhweb.info\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/434\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/tintuc6.ninhbinhweb.info\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3173"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/tintuc6.ni